NEW YORK TRAP ROCK CORPORATION, Libellant-Appellee, v. The CITY OF NEW YORK, Respondent-Appellant. No. 173. Circuit Court of Appeals, Second Circuit. Feb. 3, 1941. William C. Chanler, Corp. Counsel, of New York City (George Seagrave Franklin, of New York City, of counsel), for appellant. Hagen & Eidenbach, of New York City (Henry C. Eidenbach and Charles W. Hagen, both of New York City, of counsel), for appellee New York Trap Rock Corporation.

Before SWAN, CHASE, and CLARK, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

Decree affirmed.
